title: Nostalgia
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This small restaurant's daily menu offers at least one vegan soup and dessert daily and a vegan second dish on most days. As of May 2014, chef is vegan. Except for the daily menu (served from 11am until between 1-3pm), there are not many vegan choices.
